h1. Description

This bundle provides JMX MBeans related to the Karaf wrapper service.

In particular, an WrapperMBean is provided that can be remotely administered using a JMX client (for instance
JConsole).

With this WrapperMBean, you have the following operations available:
* install() - Install the Operating System service wrapper.
* install(String name, String displayName, String description, String startType) - Install the Operating System service
  wrapper with explicit name, display name, description, and start type.

